nely elite \u2014 who almost never trade, so their only comps are distressed sales \u2014 we show a MODELED estimate of what a player his caliber would command instead."}, "salaryDump": null, "fairContract": {"available": true, "age": 23, "valueWar": 0.2, "rate": 4710846, "terms": [{"years": 2, "endAge": 25, "projectedWar": [0.22, 0.24], "fairAav": 1858494, "totalValue": 3716989}, {"years": 3, "endAge": 26, "projectedWar": [0.22, 0.24, 0.23], "fairAav": 1858495, "totalValue": 5575484}, {"years": 4, "endAge": 27, "projectedWar": [0.22, 0.24, 0.23, 0.21], "fairAav": 1834940, "totalValue": 7339762}, {"years": 5, "endAge": 28, "projectedWar": [0.22, 0.24, 0.23, 0.21, 0.18], "fairAav": 1792543, "totalValue": 8962714}, {"years": 6, "endAge": 29, "projectedWar": [0.22, 0.24, 0.23, 0.21, 0.18, 0.15], "fairAav": 1740724, "totalValue": 10444341}, {"years": 7, "endAge": 30, "projectedWar": [0.22, 0.24, 0.23, 0.21, 0.18, 0.15, 0.11], "fairAav": 1676791, "totalValue": 11737534}, {"years": 8, "endAge": 31, "projectedWar": [0.22, 0.24, 0.23, 0.21, 0.18, 0.15, 0.11, 0.06], "fairAav": 1599398, "totalValue": 12795185}], "note": "Fair AAV = average projected annual market value over the term (aging-curve WAR walk x $4.71M/WAR, each year floored at the league minimum). Longer terms average in decline years, so the fair AAV falls. Real deals carry a term/security premium this does not model -- it is the production-fair anchor, not a prediction of the signing."}, "contractProjection": {"seasonStart": 2027, "status": "RFA", "aavLow": 974847, "aavMid": 990036, "aavHigh": 1319315, "capPctMid": 0.9, "term": 2, "comps": [{"name": "Tyler Tucker", "age": 25, "aav": 925000, "term": 2, "year": 2025, "status": "RFA"}, {"name": "Brayden Pachal", "age": 26, "aav": 1187500, "term": 2, "year": 2024, "status": "RFA"}, {"name": "Isaak Phillips", "age": 24, "aav": 812500, "term": 2, "year": 2025, "status": "RFA"}, {"name": "Kaedan Korczak", "age": 23, "aav": 825000, "term": 2, "year": 2024, "status": "RF